    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:25.370519+00:00",
    "zh": "由大语言模型(LLM)驱动的自主代理人工智能系统引入了一类新的安全、隐私和合规性挑战：一个可以调用工具、操纵数据、安装软件并与组织中的同行代理进行协调的代理"
  },
  "Bayesian predictive inference provides a principled framework for uncertainty quantification, data efficiency, and robust generalization": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:28.076373+00:00",
    "zh": "贝叶斯预测推断为不确定性量化、数据效率和鲁棒泛化提供了一个原则框架"
  },
  "Benchmark infrastructure for personally identifiable information (PII) detection remains limited: existing corpora cover few entity types, use ad hoc generation conditions, and do not show which surface conditions cause detector failures": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:42.845205+00:00",
    "zh": "用于个人身份信息（ PII ）检测的基准基础设施仍然有限：现有语料库涵盖的实体类型很少，使用临时生成条件，并且不显示导致检测器故障的表面条件"
  },
  "Block diffusion language models accelerate decoding through parallel block-wise denoising, yet whether they can be reliably scaled for long chain-of-thought (CoT) reasoning remains unresolved": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:27.671080+00:00",
    "zh": "块扩散语言模型通过并行块去噪加速解码，但它们是否可以可靠地缩放以用于长思维链（ CoT ）推理仍未解决"
  },
  "Byte-Pair Encoding tokenization is statistically efficient for vocabulary compression, but semantically blind to structured technical entities, fragmenting physical quantities, numbers, units, and symbolic expressions into lexically arbitrary subwords": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:06.873206+00:00",
    "zh": "字节对编码标记化在词汇压缩方面具有统计效率，但在语义上对结构化技术实体视而不见，将物理量、数字、单位和符号表达式分割成词汇任意子词"
  },
  "Charged-particle tracking -- reconstructing trajectories from sparse detector measurements -- is a fundamental high-energy-physics inference problem and a canonical example of learning under extreme combinatorial ambiguity": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:34.964184+00:00",
    "zh": "带电粒子跟踪--从稀疏探测器测量重建轨迹--是一个基本的高能物理推理问题，也是极端组合歧义下学习的一个典型例子"
  },
  "Continual Test-Time Adaptation (CTTA) aims to maintain model performance under evolving target domains by adapting online without labeled data": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:37.606533+00:00",
    "zh": "持续测试时间自适应（ CTTA ）旨在通过在线调整无标记数据来保持模型在不断变化的目标域下的性能"
  },
  "Decentralized finance exposes supervisors to fast-moving, networked credit risks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:17.045572+00:00",
    "zh": "去中心化金融使主管面临快速移动、网络化的信用风险"
  },
  "Deep research agents have demonstrated remarkable capabilities in autonomous information gathering and synthesis, yet their training remains constrained by the static nature of simulated environments, the limits of fact-retrieval-only task designs, and the ine": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:41.954025+00:00",
    "zh": "深度研究机构在自主信息收集和合成方面表现出非凡的能力，但他们的训练仍然受到模拟环境的静态性质，仅事实检索任务设计的局限性以及"
  },
  "Deepfakes targeting a high-profile individual, known as Person-of-Interest (POI), are a threat to modern democracies and societies": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:49.502714+00:00",
    "zh": "针对高调个人（称为利益相关者（ POI ） ）的深度伪造对现代民主和社会构成威胁"
  },
  "Existing graph-based multi-agent system (MAS) designers mainly improve collaboration by optimizing communication topologies over predefined agents, roles, or groups": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:43.696755+00:00",
    "zh": "现有的基于图形的多代理系统(MAS)设计人员主要通过优化预定义的代理、角色或组的通信拓扑来改善协作"
  },
  "Existing multi-speaker dialogue systems bind speakers to utterances through structured supervision: per-turn tags, multi-stream transcriptions, or learnable speaker embeddings": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:26.100720+00:00",
    "zh": "现有的多发言者对话系统通过结构化监督将发言者与话语绑定：每轮标签、多流转录或可学习的发言者嵌入"
  },
  "Flow matching has emerged as a standard paradigm for robotic manipulation owing to its strong expressive power for modelling complex, multimodal action distributions, alongside similar approaches like diffusion policy": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:28.984601+00:00",
    "zh": "流量匹配已经成为机器人操作的标准范例，因为它具有很强的表达能力，可以对复杂的多模态动作分布进行建模，同时还具有扩散策略等类似方法"
  },
  "Glioma segmentation in multiparametric MRI is a critical component of treatment planning": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:26.898472+00:00",
    "zh": "多参数MRI中的胶质瘤分割是治疗计划的重要组成部分"
  },
  "Human visual attention relies on structured scanpaths to efficiently process scenes, yet instilling this behavior into robot autonomy is in its infancy and hindered by the high,computational costs of existing predictive models": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:46.191849+00:00",
    "zh": "人类的视觉注意力依赖于结构化扫描路径来有效地处理场景，但是将这种行为灌输到机器人自主性中还处于起步阶段，并受到现有预测模型高昂的计算成本的阻碍"
  },
  "LLM-based coding agents need higher-level operational knowledge about a repository (which files house which subsystems, how to run the test suite, which workflows have historically led to wrong fixes) that does not exist in the code itself": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:31.714831+00:00",
    "zh": "基于LLM的编码代理需要更高级别的操作知识，了解代码本身不存在的存储库（存储哪些子系统、如何运行测试套件、哪些工作流程历来导致错误的修复）"
  },
  "Large Language Model (LLM)-based automatic Multi-Agent Systems (MAS) generation has become a crucial frontier for tackling complex tasks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:21.687366+00:00",
    "zh": "基于大语言模型（ LLM ）的自动多Agent系统（ MAS ）生成已成为处理复杂任务的关键前沿"
  },
  "Large language models (LLMs) are increasingly deployed in sensitive settings such as software engineering, where their outputs directly shape downstream artifacts": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:12.800859+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）越来越多地部署在软件工程等敏感环境中，其输出直接影响下游工件"
  },
  "Large language models (LLMs) can make clinical decision support more accessible by interpreting free-text documentation, but their direct use as diagnostic engines is limited by sensitivity to prompts, information order, and plausible but incorrect outputs": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:11.977158+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）可以通过解释自由文本文档使临床决策支持更容易获得，但它们作为诊断引擎的直接用途受到对提示、信息顺序和合理但不正确的输出的敏感度的限制"
  },
  "Latent Diffusion Models (LDMs) have become dominant in visual synthesis, but their quality-compute trade-off is largely constrained by the tokenizer's fixed compression ratio": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:39.406345+00:00",
    "zh": "潜在扩散模型（ LDM ）在视觉合成中占据主导地位，但它们的质量-计算权衡在很大程度上受到标记器固定压缩比的限制"
  },
  "Leveraging Vision Foundation Models (VFMs) for camera-to-LiDAR knowledge distillation offers a promising solution to the scarcity of annotated data needed to represent the immense geometric and kinematic diversity of real-world autonomous driving (AD)": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:38.542595+00:00",
    "zh": "利用视觉基础模型（ VFM ）进行相机到LiDAR的知识提取，为代表现实世界自动驾驶（ AD ）的巨大几何和运动多样性所需的注释数据的稀缺性提供了一个有前途的解决方案"
  },
  "Low-rank adaptation (LoRA) makes it cheap to train many domain- and task-specific language model adapters, but whether two adapters can be merged is usually discovered only after both have been fully trained and evaluated": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:23.464909+00:00",
    "zh": "低秩自适应（ LoRA ）使得训练许多特定领域和任务的语言模型适配器变得便宜，但通常只有在两个适配器都经过充分训练和评估后才能发现是否可以合并两个适配器"
  },
  "Mainstream LLM serving systems reuse prefix work mainly through paged or radix key-value (KV) caches": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:34.109260+00:00",
    "zh": "主流LLM服务系统重用前缀主要通过分页或基数键值(KV)缓存工作"
  },
  "Modern LLM training breaks a core assumption behind offline batch samplers: the true training cost of a sample is only observable after preprocessing, augmentation, templating, tokenization, and multimodal visual-token expansion": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:29.896986+00:00",
    "zh": "现代LLM培训打破了离线批量采样器背后的核心假设：样本的真实培训成本只有在预处理、增强、模板化、标记化和多模态可视化令牌扩展后才能观察到"
  },
  "Multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) enables agents to develop coordination strategies through emergent communication, but neural policies lack the formal safety guarantees required for safety-critical robotic deployment in drone swarms and autonomous veh": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:22.539936+00:00",
    "zh": "多智能体强化学习（ MARL ）使智能体能够通过紧急沟通制定协调策略，但神经政策缺乏在无人机群和自主VEH中部署安全关键机器人所需的正式安全保障"
  },
  "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) improves factual grounding, but it also lengthens prompts and raises prefill cost": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:45.277548+00:00",
    "zh": "检索增强生成（ RAG ）改善了事实基础，但也延长了提示并提高了预填充成本"
  },
  "Streaming video generation is emerging as a new serving workload in which users interact with long-lived sessions that generate video progressively, chunk by chunk": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:17.841708+00:00",
    "zh": "流媒体视频生成正在成为一种新的服务工作负载，其中用户与逐块逐渐生成视频的长寿命会话进行交互"
  },
  "Synthetic data for autonomous driving is surging, powered by diffusion models that promise scalable scene generation": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:32.575664+00:00",
    "zh": "用于自动驾驶的合成数据正在激增，由扩散模型提供支持，这些模型承诺可扩展的场景生成"
  },
  "Test-time scaling via sequential revision has emerged as a powerful paradigm for enhancing Large Language Model (LLM) reasoning": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:11.098830+00:00",
    "zh": "通过顺序修订进行测试时间缩放已成为增强大语言模型（ LLM ）推理的强大范例"
  },
  "Text-rich images often contain privacy-sensitive, transactional, or decision-relevant information": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:09.428571+00:00",
    "zh": "文字丰富的图片通常包含隐私敏感、交易或与决策相关的信息"
  },
  "The mismatch between continuous acoustic signals and discrete event-driven processing remains a fundamental bottleneck for neuromorphic speech processing": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:14.550224+00:00",
    "zh": "连续声信号和离散事件驱动处理之间的不匹配仍然是神经形态语音处理的根本瓶颈"
  },
  "This paper introduces RACL, a Reasoning-Agent Control Layer for metaheuristics": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:33.333377+00:00",
    "zh": "本文介绍了RACL ，一种用于元启发式的推理代理控制层"
  },
  "This paper studies how to scale learning-based automatic emergency braking (AEB) with massive unlabeled fleet data under production constraints": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:20.185928+00:00",
    "zh": "本文研究如何在生产约束下使用大量未标记的车队数据扩展基于学习的自动紧急制动（ AEB ）"
  },
  "To align a Large Language Model (LLM), most existing methods collect explicit human feedback and train a reward model to predict the human preference based on the response text": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:47.855989+00:00",
    "zh": "为了对齐大语言模型（ LLM ） ，大多数现有方法收集明确的人类反馈并训练奖励模型，以根据响应文本预测人类偏好"
  },
  "Training-free anomalous sound detection (ASD) scores a test clip against a memory bank of normal embeddings from a frozen pretrained audio encoder": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:18.648672+00:00",
    "zh": "无训练异常声音检测（ ASD ）根据来自冻结的预训练音频编码器的正常嵌入的存储库对测试剪辑进行评分"
  },
  "Training-free detectors of AI-generated images promise generator-agnostic deployment without classifier training, yet their reported numbers are rarely compared under a single controlled protocol": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:47.019459+00:00",
    "zh": "人工智能生成的图像的无训练检测器承诺在没有分类器训练的情况下进行与生成器无关的部署，但其报告的数量很少在单个受控协议下进行比较"
  },
  "Turkish is agglutinative: meaning is carried by morphemes, yet the subword tokenizers that drive modern language models split words by corpus statistics, fragmenting semantically loaded suffixes and -- in the case of WordPiece and rule-based analyzers -- faili": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:15.484823+00:00",
    "zh": "土耳其语是凝聚性的：意义由语素承载，但驱动现代语言模型的子词标记器通过语料库统计分割单词，分割语义加载的后缀，以及-在WordPiece和基于规则的分析器的情况下-失败"
  },
  "UAV Vision-Language Navigation (UAV-VLN) is typically formulated as a holistic search-and-reach problem, where long-range target discovery and final target approach are optimized and evaluated jointly": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:40.231796+00:00",
    "zh": "无人机视觉语言导航（ UAV-VLN ）通常被制定为一个整体搜索和到达问题，其中远程目标发现和最终目标方法被优化和评估"
  },
  "Undergraduate computer science is governed by international curricular guidelines revised about once a decade, yet programs lack a reliable, reproducible way to measure how completely they cover the current guidelines and how that coverage shifts when the guid": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:24.291598+00:00",
    "zh": "本科计算机科学由大约每十年修订一次的国际课程指南管理，但课程缺乏可靠，可重复的方法来衡量它们如何完全覆盖当前的指导方针以及当指南"
  },
  "Unlike traditional remote sensing change detection that relies on predefined categories, Open-Vocabulary Change Detection (OVCD) identifies land cover changes flexibly using arbitrary text prompts": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:41.063662+00:00",
    "zh": "与依赖预定义类别的传统遥感变化检测不同，开放式词汇表变化检测（ OVCD ）使用任意文本提示灵活识别土地覆盖变化"
  },
  "Video generative models ( VGMs) have become a new frontier that can be used not just for video generation but for a multitude of downstream tasks, including world modeling": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:19.428894+00:00",
    "zh": "视频生成模型（ VGM ）已成为一个新的前沿领域，不仅可用于视频生成，还可用于众多下游任务，包括世界建模"
  },
  "Vision Foundation Models (VFMs) with Vision Transformer (ViT) backbones, such as DINOv2, have become essential for downstream tasks like object recognition and semantic segmentation": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:08.651157+00:00",
    "zh": "具有视觉变换器（ ViT ）骨干的视觉基础模型（ VFM ） ，如DINOv2 ，已成为对象识别和语义分割等下游任务必不可少的"
  },
  "Vision-language models (VLMs) often underperform on evidence intensive tasks because decisive visual evidence are small, localized, and easy to overlook, leading to failures in evidence readout even when high-level reasoning is intact": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:35.868612+00:00",
    "zh": "视觉语言模型（ VLM ）在证据密集型任务中往往表现不佳，因为决定性的视觉证据规模小、局部化且易于忽视，即使在高层次推理完好无损的情况下，也会导致证据读取失败"
  },
  "Vision-language navigation agents achieve competitive average success on benchmark tasks, yet failures often arise through predictable trajectory-level breakdowns such as oscillation, stagnation, or inefficient detours": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:48.708798+00:00",
    "zh": "视觉语言导航代理在基准任务上取得了有竞争力的平均成功，但失败往往是通过可预测的轨迹级故障（如振荡、停滞或低效的绕行）发生的"
  },
  "Voice agents deployed in structured workflows (customer service, healthcare scheduling, account management) must handle frequent user interruptions while maintaining progress through multi-step procedures": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:16.329983+00:00",
    "zh": "部署在结构化工作流程（客户服务、医疗保健调度、帐户管理）中的语音代理必须处理频繁的用户中断，同时通过多步骤程序保持进度"
  },
  "We introduce StaminaBench, a benchmark that measures the stamina of coding agents: how many consecutive interaction turns (change requests) they can handle before failing": {
    "source": "mymemory",
